DTSTAMP:20260326T040101Z
DTSTART:20260326T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:From the Office of Councilman Kettle: \\nRight now\\\, the Offi
	ce of Planning and Community Development is putting together four specific
	 subarea plans: the Downtown Regional Plan\\\, the Northgate plan\\\, and 
	two Manufacturing-Industrial Center plans. All of these plans are intended
	 to come to Council to be voted on in late summer-early fall\\\, and you c
	an sign up here for OPCD updates. \\nIn the meantime\\\, my office will be
	 hosting several Comprehensive Plan-specific office hours in March and Apr
	il. \\nThese office hours will follow our standard rules: sign in\\\, each
	 speaker / group gets 10-15 minutes (depending on how many people have sig
	ned up)\\\, and will be first come\\\, first serve. \\nYou can use my Inst
	agram or Facebook to track updates.\n\nhttps://discovermagnolia.org/event/
	comprehensive-plan-office-hours-magnolia-public-library/\n\nFrom Discover 
	Magnolia
